About Me

Hi, I'm Jess.

I am currently a Tech Consultant at Adobe in NYC working on the Campaign team. I majored in Digital Media Design and minored in Fine Arts at the University of Pennsylvania, where I graduated from the School of Engineering in May 2019.

In my free time, I love cartooning, doodling, watching stand up, playing with my two cats, and running.

Inspired by old New Yorker cartoons, I decided to start my own cartoon instagram, Peng and Ink, a year ago as an outlet to showcase my humor and creativity. If you like cartoons or just want a laugh, feel free to check it out!

) } } export default About;
